<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>70</hymn_number>
<title>Yesu Atuchunga TZR70</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Yesu atuchunga,
 Mchunga wetu,
 Naye atufuta
 Machozi yetu;
 Mkononi mwake
 Hatuna hofu,
 Daima twapata
 Kwake wokovu.

[V2]
 Yesu atuchunga
 Tumemjua,
 Na sauti yake
 Twaitambua;
 Naye akituonya
 Ni kwa upole,
 Tu kondoo zake
 Hata milele.

[V3]
 Yesu atuchunga;
 Aliwafia
 Kondoo wakubwa
 Na wana pia;
 Kwamba awajua,
 Kondoo zake,
 Hutiwa alama
 Ya damu yake.

[V4]
 Yesu atuchunga;
 Mikono yake
 Imewaambata
 Kondoo zake;
 Hapati wadhuru
 Adui yule,
 Yesu awalinda.
 Hata milele</lyrics>
</song>